01:11.104 --> 01:12.906 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Buckle up.

01:13.006 --> 01:17.811 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
JOHN YANG: Perhaps keeping an eye on Wisconsin,
where election officials approved a recount.

01:17.911 --> 01:24.284 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
