01:43.804 --> 01:46.440 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
JILL STEIN, Green Party Presidential Candidate:
I don't think that's likely, and this is not

01:46.540 --> 01:49.643 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
