and the intellect and the integrity of Donald

02:25.779 --> 02:30.684 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Trump, now our president-elect, would be given
the most prominent Cabinet post of all, secretary

02:30.784 --> 02:32.119 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of state.

02:32.219 --> 02:34.788 align:left position:62.5%,start line:86.67% size:37.5%
JOHN YANG: A message she said she's also delivered
in private.

02:34.888 --> 02:39.459 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
