03:03.016 --> 03:06.653 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Cuba is in mourning today for its late leader
Fidel Castro.

03:06.753 --> 03:10.991 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
The 90-year-old died Friday night, after being
in ill health for years.

03:11.091 --> 03:15.762 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Today, thousands lined up in Havana's Plaza
of the Revolution to pay their respects at

03:15.862 --> 03:19.833 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
a memorial for the man who ruled their countryfor nearly half-a-century.

03:19.933 --> 03:25.505 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
We will have more on Castro's death and what
it may mean for Cuba's future later in the

03:25.605 --> 03:27.541 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
program.

03:27.641 --> 03:32.946 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Back in this country, a knife-wielding attacker
wounded at least 11 people at Ohio State University

03:33.046 --> 03:34.448 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in Columbus.

03:34.548 --> 03:37.918 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Authorities said the man was a student there
and of Somali descent.

03:38.018 --> 03:43.356 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
He rammed his car into a crowd, and then stabbed
people with a butcher knife, before being

03:43.457 --> 03:45.559 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
shot dead by police.

03:45.659 --> 03:50.530 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Dozens of officers rushed to the scene, while
the campus of some 60,000 students was put

03:50.630 --> 03:52.265 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
on lockdown for several hours.

03:52.365 --> 03:54.167 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

03:54.267 --> 03:55.402 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
MICHAEL DRAKE, President, Ohio State University:
We don't know anything that would link this

03:55.502 --> 03:56.870 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to any community.

03:56.970 --> 03:59.039 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
We certainly don't any evidence that would
say that is the case.

03:59.139 --> 04:04.778 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
And what we want to do is really unify together,
support each other, do our best to support

04:04.878 --> 04:08.748 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
those who were injured in their recovery,
and then allow the investigation to take place.

04:08.849 --> 04:13.753 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
JOHN YANG: Police are now investigating the
suspect's motive, including whether it was

04:13.854 --> 04:15.655 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
an act of terrorism.

04:15.755 --> 04:19.759 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
