will be allowed to represent himself at his

04:19.860 --> 04:21.094 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
trial.

04:21.194 --> 04:23.630 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Dylann Roof made that request, against his
lawyers' advice.

04:23.730 --> 04:27.734 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
The trial judge granted it, but called Roof's
decision unwise.

04:27.834 --> 04:32.172 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
