04:35.175 --> 04:38.512 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Federal prosecutors are seeking the death
penalty.

04:38.612 --> 04:43.783 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
And stocks tumbled on Wall Street today, as
the post-election market rally appeared to

04:43.884 --> 04:45.385 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
ease.

